		<header2>What is TapTools?</header2>
		<body>
			TapTools is a set of objects and extensions to Cycling &apos;74&apos;s Max, MSP, and Jitter environments. These objects 
			enhance and extend what you are able to do within Max, and make some patching tasks easier. There are many
			objects for processing audio, video, and data. TapTools is developed and maintained by 
			<a href="http://74objects.com">74 Objects</a> who used TapTools as the basis for the 
			<a href="http://74objects.com/hipno/">Hipno</a> plug-ins, which were marketed by Cycling &apos;74.
			<br /><br />
		</body>

